✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: I love math related clashes :D

✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: Did the necessary modification, pretty cool even if you dont know a lot about maths.

Game modes
* Reverse Mode may be enabled.

Goal section
* I don't know what a "parametric line" is.

* I don't understand the entire instruction.

* Please describe the output format.

Input section
* Please split the description into Line 1 and Line 2. In particular, points A and B should be defined in the new descriptions.

* Please mention the variable format and type in each line (3 space-separated integers).

Output section
* xA, yA, zA and AB are undefined. And I don't understand what x(AB), y(AB) or z(AB) are.

Constraints section
* No variable [[a]] or [[b]] has been defined.

Cases
* The first pair of cases are the same. Please revise them so that they are different.

Stub generator
* Please use loopline instead of string for both lines.

* Please add a write statement (e.g. "write answer").

Thanks.
